name: Verify that the Underwriter Manager column is shown in mentioned Policy Overview reports whereever there is a Underwriter column next to it and populate the Underwriter Manager values

testSteps.description: 1: Verify that the Underwriter Manager column is shown in mentioned Policy Overview reports whereever there is a Underwriter column next to it and populate the Underwriter Manager values ({Reports=In-Force Policies})

children.description: Given underwriter is on home page of PAS
And user Navigates to Reports
And select Policy 'Policy' from Reports
And select Reports 'In-Force Policies' from Policy
When user select Underwriting Overview 'Underwriting Overview' from VIEW
Then the field 'UNDERWRITER MANAGER' should be displayed next to 'UNDERWRITER NAME'

testSteps.description: 2: Verify that the Underwriter Manager column is shown in mentioned Policy Overview reports whereever there is a Underwriter column next to it and populate the Underwriter Manager values ({Reports=Cancelled Policies})
